{{#if isMonitoringStation}}
  <h3 class="heading-large">{{#if isRiverLevelStation}}Depth{{else}}Water level{{/if}} and flow estimates for the monitoring station at {{stationName}}</h3>
  <p>The Environment Agency uses 3 risk scenarios to estimate the {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}depth{{else}}level{{/if}} and flow of water that could occur at this location in any given year.</p>

  <h4 class="heading-medium">
    {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}Depth{{else}}Level{{/if}} estimates at this monitoring station
  </h4>

  <h5 class="heading-small">
    High chance scenario
  </h5>
  <p>There's a high chance (over 3.3%) that {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}water depth{{else}}the water level{{/if}} will reach {{depth30}}m</p>

  <h5 class="heading-small">
    Medium chance scenario
  </h5>
  <p>There's a medium chance (over 1%) that {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}water depth{{else}}the water level{{/if}} will reach {{depth100}}m</p>

  <h5 class="heading-small">
    Low chance scenario
  </h5>
  <p>There's a low chance (under 1%) that {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}water depth{{else}}the water level{{/if}} will reach {{depth1000}}m</p>

  {{#if isRiverLevelStation}}
    <h4 class="heading-medium">
      Flow estimates at this monitoring station
    </h4>

    <h5 class="heading-small">
      High chance scenario
    </h5>
    <p>There's a high chance (over 3.3%) that the flow will reach {{flow30}} cubic metres per second.</p>

    <h5 class="heading-small">
      Medium chance scenario
    </h5>
    <p>There's a medium chance (over 1%) that the flow will reach {{flow100}} cubic metres per second.</p>

    <h5 class="heading-small">
      Low chance scenario
    </h5>
    <p>There's a low chance (under 1%) that the flow will reach {{flow1000}} cubic metres per second.</p>
  {{/if}}
{{else if isRiskDescription}}
  {{#if isRiversOrSeas}}
    <div class="rivers-seas {{id}}">
      {{> ../../../views/partials/risk-types/rivers-seas.html}}
    </div>
  {{else if isSurfaceWater}}
    <div class="surface-water {{id}}">
      {{> ../../../views/partials/risk-types/surface-water.html}}
    </div>
  {{/if}}
{{/if}}
